{"tid":1521980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝點藍色水見到藍絲同黑道就潑埋醒佢","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:55:42.000Z","uid":263708,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57c466d7839eb4016bd112968fd3f4ac27381b51","tid":1521980,"uid":263708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:48:58.000Z","msg":"好計嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c9e847d1db864471c1bd31ff180c83d8899854","tid":1521980,"uid":184379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57c466d7839eb4016bd112968fd3f4ac27381b51","tid":1521980,"uid":263708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:48:58.000Z","msg":"好計嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c425660b8465c999855db64539b452c6c187e593","tid":1521980,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span>"},{"pid":"38511790a86de405bac17f33663f54e12f84e838","tid":1521980,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"天才，佢地一定唔識點洗走啲色"},{"pid":"859e5c2532fc259e30eb4b54ebc07db98af268cd","tid":1521980,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021d940d4389f20132a66da07c9ecd3f44442cc4","tid":1521980,"uid":180663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}